   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Alkimos, collector of the quarter (tax) on the salters and general dealers of Oxyrhyncha for the 4th year to Androniskos son of Horion, greeting. I have received from you the contribution for Mesore and the five intercalary days of the said year, and make no claim on you. The fourth year, Mesore 15.</ab>
